txt.en: 'You have done much for the Gondorian army. We will take back this city!'
Edenos is at the Palace of Eldacar.\n\nYou should speak to Edenos.
The Ornendil Bridge is located in Northern Osgiliath over the Anduin River.\n\nYou should defend the centre of the Ornendil Bridge.
Edenos has tasked you with defending the Ornendil Bridge from enemy who is trying to retake it.
Do not leave the centre of the bridge
Defend the centre of the Ornendil Bridge
You have left the bridge unguarded
The Ornendil Bridge is located in Northern Osgiliath over the Anduin River.\n\nYou should keep your post and defend the centre of the Ornendil Bridge.
Keep your post and defend the centre of the bridge
You have successfully defended the Ornendil Bridge
'The enemy is trying to capture the Ornendil Bridge! You must defend the centre of the bridge with your life.\n\n'We cannot afford to lose this key defensive point over the Anduin! For Gondor!'
